{"tid":540552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"駕駛學院考牌女「肥佬」 發難佔領馬路","createTime":"2018-01-25T15:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T00:17:14.000Z","uid":20933,"like":195,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"8a400cac471c09ebad6788090c24b156ecbbad1f","tid":540552,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T15:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180125/large/1516886134_5e99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180125%2Flarge%2F1516886134_5e99.jpg&h=870a1e3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙田駕駛學院發生「佔領」馬路事件，下午近4時，一名33歲姓朱女子考完中型貨車路試後，返回駕駛學院，結果考試「肥佬」(不合格)，她與考牌官爭執，其間情緒激動，衝出馬路截停其他考牌車輛，並揚言「要死」，駕駛學院職員見狀報警求助。警員接報到場，將案件列作企圖自殺案，召救護車把女事主送往醫院檢查。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"5d69214f3afd1bcaad0f61473658ce3a0305c53c","tid":540552,"uid":43231,"like":274,"dislike":3,"score":271,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T15:18:23.000Z","msg":"嗌自殺就覺得可以攞到牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7295f485ac95057041d49f14ceff69afc848a4b8","tid":540552,"uid":97814,"like":26,"dislike":259,"score":-233,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T15:19:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62862d4685b3000bca49d6166c4486727e7e91e0","tid":540552,"uid":15739,"like":221,"dislike":0,"score":221,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T15:20:28.000Z","msg":"貼埋求助熱線笑左"},{"pid":"e4de15a7ff40cacad9102353fd5f7734c0c98002","tid":540552,"uid":90644,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T15:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好驚我考試個日都有呢d人"},{"pid":"0665765cfc2d9310dee4c300f40fffbbcb77cf5e","tid":540552,"uid":23433,"l